OL,3,CToy car bursts into flames killing
OL,4,Ccats and destroying home
OL,6,FA mother from Hampshire is warning
OL,7,Fpeople about the dangers of lithium-
OL,8,Fion batteries following a devastating
OL,9,Fflat fire.
OL,11,FMolly's two-year-old daughter had an
OL,12,Felectric toy car which was on charge
OL,13,Fwhen it suddenly burst into flames.
OL,15,FMolly said the flames were "crawling
OL,16,Fup the wall" in the lounge and the
OL,17,Fpair were forced to flee their home.
OL,19,FThey were able to escape but their two
OL,20,Fcats were killed and their home was
OL,21,Fdestroyed.
