OL,6,FSix months on and they're yet to move
OL,7,Fback in.
OL,9,FMolly says she doesn't want anyone
OL,10,Felse to suffer, adding: "It's just
OL,11,Fspreading awareness of how to be
OL,12,Fcareful and just knowing the dangers
OL,13,Fbecause I wouldn't have thought this
OL,14,Fwould have happened at all."
OL,16,FHampshire and Isle of Wight Fire and
OL,17,FRescue Service says there has been a
OL,18,Fhuge surge in battery-related fires.
