OL,6,FIn 2019 there was one recorded fire
OL,7,Fwithin Hampshire and the Isle of Wight
OL,8,Fbut this year there has been 36 so far.
OL,10,FLithium-ion batteries are rechargeable
OL,11,Fbatteries which are found in electric
OL,12,Fbikes, scooters, cars, laptops,
OL,13,Ftablets and mobile phones.
OL,15,FThe fire service says it's important
OL,16,Fthat the products people buy are safe.
